WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.670
Based on and inspired by the teachings
of Shri Mataji Nirmala Devi, this series

00:00:02.670 --> 00:00:05.574
aims to explore the evolutionary relationship
between two interconnected domains

00:00:05.574 --> 00:00:07.844
expressing human awareness
at the gross and subtle levels.

00:00:07.844 --> 00:00:11.115
It endeavors to elucidate this complex interplay
between the current scientific understanding

00:00:11.115 --> 00:00:13.919
of human neuroanatomy; the autonomic
nervous system in particular,

00:00:13.919 --> 00:00:16.923
and the so-called subtle system as described
in the traditional literature on yoga.

00:00:16.923 --> 00:00:19.961
Ultimately, the series tries to bring 
its viewers along this exploratory journey

00:00:19.961 --> 00:00:23.500
to experience these relationships through meditation
as taught by Shri Mataji Nirmala Devi.

00:00:53.040 --> 00:00:55.600
Thanks everyone for joining us today.

00:00:55.600 --> 00:00:59.440
In our previous episode, we
started on an exploration

00:00:59.440 --> 00:01:03.680
into the fascinating intersection
of neuroscience and spirituality

00:01:03.680 --> 00:01:07.840
with Dr. Ashish Pradhan,
who is a distinguished leader in neurology

00:01:07.840 --> 00:01:11.680
and cardiovascular medicine,
renowned for his cutting-edge work

00:01:11.680 --> 00:01:14.720
and strategic leadership
in patient-centric care.

00:01:14.720 --> 00:01:20.080
He emphasized the importance of understanding
the complexities of the nervous system

00:01:20.080 --> 00:01:24.880
as a foundation for exploring
the spiritual aspects of being human.

00:01:24.880 --> 00:01:29.680
Dr. Pradhan also talked to us
about the brain's evolutionary journey,

00:01:29.680 --> 00:01:35.280
highlighting the fascinating adaptations
that have shaped its structure and function.

00:01:35.280 --> 00:01:40.400
And today we welcome all of you
to this second episode of our enlightening series

00:01:40.400 --> 00:01:43.200
with the esteemed Dr. Ashish Pradhan.

00:01:43.200 --> 00:01:46.880
Today we're taking this exploration
even deeper.

00:01:46.880 --> 00:01:50.640
So get ready for another
thought-provoking conversation

00:01:50.640 --> 00:01:55.360
as we continue to bridge the worlds
of science and spirituality.

00:01:55.360 --> 00:01:57.840
Welcome, Dr. Pradhan.

00:01:57.840 --> 00:01:58.400
Thank you.

