Thank you for the kind words, Monikaji.

00:02:00.320 --> 00:02:01.920
Happy to be back.

00:02:01.920 --> 00:02:07.600
We definitely look forward to learning
a lot with you in this yet another episode.

00:02:07.600 --> 00:02:10.560
So, Dr. Pradhan, like I said,
in our previous episode,

00:02:10.560 --> 00:02:14.640
we delved into the intricate workings
of the human nervous system,

00:02:14.640 --> 00:02:16.480
the autonomic nervous system,

00:02:16.480 --> 00:02:19.360
