00:19:10.480 --> 00:19:13.280
manifest different qualities.

00:19:13.280 --> 00:19:21.280
And it is through the energy center -
that is, the chakra -

00:19:21.280 --> 00:19:26.960
that the energy transmitted to the plexus
governs the functioning

00:19:26.960 --> 00:19:34.320
of that particular organ system or organs
within the remit of that plexus.

00:19:34.320 --> 00:19:38.320
So, as we will see as we move along,
there are specific plexuses

00:19:38.320 --> 00:19:40.640
that look after specific organs.

00:19:40.640 --> 00:19:42.320
The reason why this is important

00:19:42.320 --> 00:19:44.880
is to understand both the
physiology and the pathology.

00:19:44.880 --> 00:19:47.600
The physiology is very simple,
as we just expressed.

00:19:47.600 --> 00:19:53.600
Energy transmitted to the plexus
and therefore the functioning of the organ system.

00:19:54.800 --> 00:20:01.200
Equally important, if
the energy center is overused,

00:20:01.200 --> 00:20:03.520
there is a finite amount of energy

00:20:03.520 --> 00:20:08.080
that is present at each
of the individual chakra levels

00:20:08.080 --> 00:20:09.840
when an individual takes birth.

00:20:09.840 --> 00:20:15.920
And throughout our life, we keep on expending
