00:20:28.960 --> 00:20:35.600
If that energy is not used
in a wise and an optimal manner,

00:20:35.600 --> 00:20:39.120
then it places strain on that chakra.

00:20:39.120 --> 00:20:42.480
That strain is then reflected
at the level of the plexus

00:20:42.480 --> 00:20:44.160
because there is an imbalance.

00:20:44.160 --> 00:20:47.440
The key to understanding everything
is the balance of this ecosystem.

00:20:47.440 --> 00:20:51.280
And if that plexus gets into a state
of imbalance, quote-unquote.

00:20:52.160 --> 00:20:54.080
Medicine doesn't 
easily explain this,

00:20:54.080 --> 00:20:56.240
but at the spiritual level, 
we can explain it

00:20:56.240 --> 00:20:59.440
through our growth in our
self-awareness through Sahaj.

00:20:59.440 --> 00:21:03.440
If the plexus gets imbalanced,
then the organ systems it governs

00:21:03.440 --> 00:21:04.880
get imbalanced as well.

00:21:04.880 --> 00:21:07.840
Which - in other words -
is what we mean by imbalance?

00:21:07.840 --> 00:21:12.560
Imbalance implies the beginning
of a pathological state,

00:21:12.560 --> 00:21:17.600
which may or may not be easily detectable,
but it starts at a very subtle level,

00:21:17.600 --> 00:21:22.720
and then over a period of time,
it manifests as gross pathology.

00:21:22.720 --> 00:21:27.840
And that is why it is important
to understand the governance structure

00:21:27.840 --> 00:21:33.760
from the energy center, that is the chakra,
to the plexus, to the organ system.

00:21:33.760 --> 00:21:38.560
Doctor, from what you mentioned, it seems like
there has to be a wise use

00:21:38.560 --> 00:21:42.560
of the finite energy that we are born with.

