If you can help us understand
what does it mean to use that energy wisely

00:21:46.480 --> 00:21:50.800
or discreetly so that we don't get
our chakras out of balance?

00:21:50.800 --> 00:21:55.240
Let's take an example of
a heart chakra,

00:21:55.240 --> 00:22:02.000
the one that governs the cardiac plexus
and our cardiovascular system,

00:22:02.000 --> 00:22:03.920
but basically the cardiac system.

00:22:03.920 --> 00:22:07.840
For example, if we overwork,
if we overstrain ourselves,

00:22:07.840 --> 00:22:12.960
we know that we are pursuing something,
maybe it's a career opportunity,

00:22:12.960 --> 00:22:16.960
we want to work, and everybody wants
to get ahead in life, and that's okay.

00:22:16.960 --> 00:22:23.280
The question is, is your ambition,
is your drive putting you in a place

00:22:23.280 --> 00:22:27.600
where you can actually feel
that you are under stress,

00:22:27.600 --> 00:22:29.920
and that stress,
at some point,

00:22:29.920 --> 00:22:32.880
is manifesting in the form
of essential hypertension.

00:22:32.880 --> 00:22:35.360
Your systolic is going up,
your diastolic is going up,

00:22:35.360 --> 00:22:40.800
at a certain age or whatever the case may be;
then knowingly doing it,

00:22:40.800 --> 00:22:44.000
or continuing to do it,
is being unwise about it,

00:22:44.000 --> 00:22:48.400
because now we should know.
Most people don't have knowledge

00:22:48.400 --> 00:22:52.800
about the chakras, but they do understand
blood pressure or hypertension—

00:22:52.800 --> 00:22:56.640
because, potentially, it's a silent thing.
But if you get the symptoms,

00:22:56.640 --> 00:22:58.960
and if you are diagnosed with it,
that's different.

00:22:58.960 --> 00:23:04.400
So, this is what we mean by being wise about it:
that whatever your drives in life,

00:23:04.400 --> 00:23:09.200
whatever your desires,
wisdom, which is, again, an innate quality

00:23:09.200 --> 00:23:14.000
that comes to us from the first energy center,
which we shall be talking about shortly,

00:23:14.000 --> 00:23:19.360
needs to manifest itself
in both our desires as well as our actions,

00:23:19.360 --> 00:23:22.880
because otherwise the system
goes out of that.

00:23:22.880 --> 00:23:27.440
The energy center for that particular organ,
or for that particular system,

00:23:27.440 --> 00:23:33.280
can start manifesting in ways
that we now describe as, maybe, diseases

00:23:33.280 --> 00:23:36.400
or disorders of the human body.

