And what the Higgs boson proved
was that energy somehow imparts properties

00:28:00.640 --> 00:28:05.200
to electromagnetic particles,
or at that quantum level,

00:28:05.200 --> 00:28:09.840
in that quantum state,
that gives them mass.

00:28:09.840 --> 00:28:14.000
Mass, in turn, produces gravity.

00:28:14.000 --> 00:28:15.200
What is gravity?

00:28:15.200 --> 00:28:17.040
It's the curvature of space-time.

00:28:17.040 --> 00:28:22.480
So, whatever mass you have,
it leads to that part of gravity,

00:28:22.480 --> 00:28:25.520
and that is a constant.

00:28:25.520 --> 00:28:31.760
Newton showed us that there is
a constant in terms of gravity.

00:28:31.760 --> 00:28:34.400
Why is that important?

00:28:34.400 --> 00:28:41.280
This is important to know
that energy preceded the creation of matter,

00:28:41.280 --> 00:28:46.800
and that helps us to understand
our subtle system and also our chakras.

00:28:46.800 --> 00:28:52.560
The Muladhara chakra,
or the first energy center, represents

00:28:52.560 --> 00:29:00.880
that first primordial step after the Big Bang,
or around that time, or just following that,

00:29:00.880 --> 00:29:06.400
as this heat was released,
and then that heat started slowly,

00:29:06.400 --> 00:29:08.640
as the system started coalescing,

00:29:08.640 --> 00:29:15.520
leading to the formation of the big stars.
And within the cores of these big stars,

00:29:15.520 --> 00:29:18.960
you had fusion reactions
where hydrogen and helium nuclei

00:29:18.960 --> 00:29:22.240
started coming together,
and elements were formed.

00:29:22.240 --> 00:29:24.640
And a key element was carbon.

00:29:24.640 --> 00:29:27.680
And carbon, as we know, is tetravalent.

00:29:27.680 --> 00:29:32.320
It has four valencies,
and it is the basic molecule

00:29:32.320 --> 00:29:35.760
that leads to formation
of organic compounds.

00:29:35.760 --> 00:29:40.480
And the human being,
or everything that we see around us,

00:29:40.480 --> 00:29:42.720
animals, plants, whatever,

00:29:42.720 --> 00:29:46.160
is a product of that organic chemistry.

00:29:46.160 --> 00:29:50.160
So this element, carbon,
which has four valencies,

00:29:50.160 --> 00:29:54.400
is also interestingly represented
in some ways as the swastika,

00:29:54.400 --> 00:29:57.360
which is a very traditional ancient symbol.

00:29:57.360 --> 00:30:00.800
Unfortunately, in the last century,
it got a very bad reputation,

00:30:00.800 --> 00:30:02.320
but it has nothing to do with it.

00:30:02.320 --> 00:30:06.880
It has been recognized as a symbol
of auspiciousness and purity

00:30:08.240 --> 00:30:10.960
and everything that goes with it.

00:30:10.960 --> 00:30:13.200
So, that is how it starts.

00:30:13.200 --> 00:30:14.800
So, this is the Muladhara chakra.

00:30:14.800 --> 00:30:21.440
The Muladhara chakra is the fulcrum,
literally the support of the entire system,

00:30:21.440 --> 00:30:30.160
and it is governed by an aspect of divinity
whose manifestation is primordial innocence.

00:30:30.160 --> 00:30:34.240
So, once again, to recap,
you have energy,

00:30:34.240 --> 00:30:40.640
that is the primordial energy
that somehow imparted its properties

00:30:40.640 --> 00:30:45.680
to electromagnetic particles
that created mass, and that mass led to gravity.

00:30:45.680 --> 00:30:48.960
And without gravity,
we would not have existed,

00:30:48.960 --> 00:30:50.880
because otherwise we would have just been,

00:30:50.880 --> 00:30:54.480
like electrons spinning
forever at the speed of light.

00:30:54.480 --> 00:30:58.960
And that gravity is also kept
at a very specific constant,

00:30:58.960 --> 00:31:02.480
because if that constant were to be
a little less or a little more

00:31:02.480 --> 00:31:08.480
we would have
just collapsed together into

00:31:08.480 --> 00:31:12.880
a hyperdense kind of matter
that would be impossible to define;

00:31:12.880 --> 00:31:15.920
or if it had been less,
we would have just been flying into space.

00:31:15.920 --> 00:31:22.160
Muladhara chakra is very important
because it represents that primordial purity

00:31:22.160 --> 00:31:28.640
of the power that created us,
and at a gross level, it is represented

00:31:28.640 --> 00:31:30.480
by the pelvic plexus.

