00:32:49.600 --> 00:32:53.920
that literally sits above it,
but the Muladhara chakra provides

00:32:53.920 --> 00:32:59.760
the support to it all, and its main function
is to provide gravity,

00:32:59.760 --> 00:33:04.400
and through that gravity, it allows
the support of the entire system.

00:33:04.400 --> 00:33:11.840
It is an extraordinarily important
energy center to be aware of.

