00:36:11.120 --> 00:36:16.240
that we otherwise cannot at a sensory level,
and that is very important.

00:36:16.240 --> 00:36:21.440
Biologically, it's interesting
that it may not be

00:36:21.440 --> 00:36:25.920
the Kundalini energy per se,
but the Kundalini energy —

00:36:25.920 --> 00:36:30.320
the fact that it allows an evolution —
bears an interesting parallel

00:36:30.320 --> 00:36:34.640
to the double helical structure
of the DNA molecule.

00:36:34.640 --> 00:36:41.040
The DNA molecule, which exists
within every cell and is the fundamental unit

00:36:41.040 --> 00:36:45.680
of all living organisms in every cell,
consists of two strands

00:36:45.680 --> 00:36:48.080
that spiral around each other.

00:36:48.080 --> 00:36:54.560
One goes up, one goes down,
and it contains the genetic code within itself,

00:36:54.560 --> 00:37:00.240
and the reason why, as the founder of Sahaja,
Shri Mataji, once explained, it is helical

00:37:00.240 --> 00:37:07.040
is because a helical movement allows you,
if you move it, to arrive at a higher plane.

00:37:07.040 --> 00:37:11.200
Circular movement allows you
to only come back to the starting point,

00:37:11.200 --> 00:37:14.000
but a helical movement allows you to rise up.

00:37:14.000 --> 00:37:16.000
That's why you have a spiral staircase.

00:37:16.640 --> 00:37:21.840
So, in a kind of analogous fashion,
the Kundalini energy allows us,

00:37:21.840 --> 00:37:26.960
when it uncoils and as it rises,
to raise our consciousness.

00:37:26.960 --> 00:37:34.160
This is present in every human being,
and it is also called the mother energy.

00:37:34.160 --> 00:37:39.600
It is your individual mother
because this is the energy that knows best

00:37:40.880 --> 00:37:46.640
what is good for you, what is best for you.
And it is a female energy

00:37:46.640 --> 00:37:50.560
that resides within each one of us,
dormant in the sacrum.

00:37:50.560 --> 00:37:52.480
And it is the awakening of this energy

00:37:52.480 --> 00:37:56.800
which is the ultimate object
of all yoga practices.

00:37:56.800 --> 00:38:01.440
In fact, yoga is defined as the awakening
of this energy and its piercing

00:38:01.440 --> 00:38:06.080
through the fontanel area,
and the awakening of the limbic system.

00:38:06.080 --> 00:38:11.440
So, that's the Kundalini energy,
which resides in the sacrum,

00:38:11.440 --> 00:38:16.480
and which certain systems of medicine,
particularly in the past, were kind of aware of.

00:38:16.480 --> 00:38:20.480
But it is extraordinarily challenging
to awaken that energy,

00:38:20.480 --> 00:38:25.680
to make it uncoil itself
and rise through the Sushumna Nadi,

00:38:25.680 --> 00:38:31.040
which, at a gross level,

00:38:31.040 --> 00:38:34.080
is represented by
the parasympathetic nervous system.

00:38:34.640 --> 00:38:37.280
So, you mentioned every human being
has this energy,

00:38:37.280 --> 00:38:41.360
and you also mentioned that this energy
helps us raise our consciousness.

00:38:41.360 --> 00:38:47.360
So, I guess my question is then,
why does every human being not evolve

00:38:47.360 --> 00:38:48.960
up to a certain level of consciousness?

00:38:48.960 --> 00:38:51.840
Why is that different?

00:38:51.840 --> 00:38:53.680
That's again a wonderful question.

00:38:53.680 --> 00:39:00.480
The reason is that this energy is a power
that can be awakened, or is awakened,

00:39:00.480 --> 00:39:07.360
only through the grace of a master.
And unless and until there is a master

00:39:07.360 --> 00:39:11.680
who has the, quote-unquote, authority
or the ability to awaken it,

00:39:11.680 --> 00:39:13.600
this energy does not rise.

00:39:13.600 --> 00:39:17.760
This energy, let's just say,
has a mind of its own;

00:39:17.760 --> 00:39:20.640
that is because it is of divine origin.

00:39:20.640 --> 00:39:24.480
It is divinity personified
within a human being,

00:39:24.480 --> 00:39:29.680
and that cannot be raised;
that cannot come up;

00:39:29.680 --> 00:39:35.520
it doesn't uncoil itself and start rising
just because somebody wants it to be so.

00:39:35.520 --> 00:39:41.440
It has to happen, or it can only happen,
if that individual, that said individual,

00:39:41.440 --> 00:39:49.280
comes in contact with a person who is a master
and whose own energy is awakened to a state

00:39:49.280 --> 00:39:54.640
that can then allow for that other individual,
who doesn't have it awakened,

00:39:54.640 --> 00:39:56.320
to be able to be awakened.

00:39:56.320 --> 00:39:58.080
We call it having a guru.

00:39:58.080 --> 00:40:02.720
It's a kind of traditional way of saying it,
but it is only through the grace of the guru—

00:40:02.720 --> 00:40:09.440
of a true guru, a primordial,
a person who is truly a true master,

00:40:09.440 --> 00:40:16.880
who has nothing but pure benevolence
in his or her heart towards this other individual

00:40:16.880 --> 00:40:21.360
can facilitate the awakening of this inner energy,

00:40:21.360 --> 00:40:24.960
which is very, very relatively
straightforward in Sahaj,

00:40:24.960 --> 00:40:28.400
but that experience we can have
after this session,

00:40:28.400 --> 00:40:33.600
as the session that is led
by Shri Mataji herself.

00:40:33.600 --> 00:40:35.120
That's what I was going to say.

00:40:35.120 --> 00:40:39.440
I think it is, on that note,
perfect time for our audiences

00:40:39.440 --> 00:40:44.720
to have that experience and then,
just follow the instructions that the founder has,

00:40:44.720 --> 00:40:47.680
because, like you mentioned, there has to be
some expert or guru

00:40:47.680 --> 00:40:52.000
who has to be able to do this for you.
And I would like to thank you, Dr. Ashish,

00:40:52.000 --> 00:40:55.440
for your time today,
and we look forward to talking to you again

00:40:55.440 --> 00:40:58.400
on the next energy center
in our subtle system,

00:40:58.400 --> 00:41:00.640
but thanks again for your time today.

00:41:00.640 --> 00:41:01.440
Thank you very much.

00:41:01.440 --> 00:41:02.160
Great questions.

00:41:02.160 --> 00:41:03.040
Enjoyed it.

00:41:03.040 --> 00:41:03.360
Thank you.

