I hope everybody enjoys
the meditation session as well.

00:41:06.720 --> 00:41:08.440
Yes, we do hope that.

00:41:13.000 --> 00:41:17.920
Shri Mataji: Called as the Muladhara chakra,
which manifests the pelvic plexus outside.

00:41:17.920 --> 00:41:26.240
Now, this center is placed below the Kundalini,
which is placed in the sacrum bone.

00:41:26.240 --> 00:41:30.160
This is called sacrum
because it is a sacred bone.

00:41:30.160 --> 00:41:36.640
In this bone lies the Kundalini,
the residual power of our germination.

00:41:36.640 --> 00:41:42.320
During the process of Kundalini awakening,
you can see the pulsation down here.

00:41:42.320 --> 00:41:46.400
You can also, through a stethoscope,
see the rising of the Kundalini,

00:41:46.400 --> 00:41:53.120
and you can see the pulsation in the backbone
till it reaches here in the fontanel bone area,

00:41:53.120 --> 00:41:55.040
where it breaks through.

00:41:55.040 --> 00:41:59.200
At that point,
you do not feel any pulsation.

00:41:59.200 --> 00:42:03.440
As soon as this happens,
from your hands, a cool breeze starts to flow.

00:42:03.440 --> 00:42:07.120
You can feel it on your fingers,
as shown here.

00:42:07.120 --> 00:42:12.240
These are the terminal points
of the sympathetic nervous system within us.

00:42:12.240 --> 00:42:17.680
These represent all the centers
that are inside us,

00:42:17.680 --> 00:42:24.083
and you start feeling them on your fingers
as absolutely your own experience.

00:42:33.120 --> 00:42:36.480
Keep your eyes closed.

00:42:36.480 --> 00:42:41.360
First of all, please put your right hand
on your heart.

00:42:41.360 --> 00:42:45.360
All the time the left hand is towards Me.

00:42:45.360 --> 00:42:55.680
Now, here you have to say in your heart,
with all sincerity, Mother, am I the Spirit?

00:42:55.680 --> 00:42:58.320
Ask the question three times
in your heart.

00:42:58.320 --> 00:43:02.430
This is a very fundamental question.

00:43:19.520 --> 00:43:27.680
Now bring the right hand
on to the left hand side of your stomach,

00:43:27.680 --> 00:43:31.600
in the upper part.

00:43:31.600 --> 00:43:32.960
Here press it.

00:43:32.960 --> 00:43:41.440
Now this is the center of your mastery,
your guidance, your guru Tattva, as they say.

00:43:41.440 --> 00:43:45.840
So ask a question,
Mother, am I my own master?

00:43:45.840 --> 00:43:48.160
This is the question to be asked
three times.

00:43:48.160 --> 00:43:53.991
Mother, am I my own master?

00:44:05.760 --> 00:44:13.920
Now bring your right hand down below
in the lower part of the abdomen.

00:44:13.920 --> 00:44:21.600
Now this is the center from which
all the Divine work is done,

00:44:21.600 --> 00:44:24.400
all the pure work is done.

00:44:24.400 --> 00:44:29.520
So to ask six times,
because this center has got six petals,

00:44:29.520 --> 00:44:35.200
Mother, please give me pure knowledge.

00:44:35.200 --> 00:44:38.400
Six times you just ask.

00:44:38.400 --> 00:44:43.631
As a result of this asking
the Kundalini starts getting awakened.

00:44:54.511 --> 00:44:59.280
Now to help the Kundalini to rise
you have to cooperate with Her.

00:44:59.280 --> 00:45:03.440
So please put your right hand
on the left hand side

00:45:03.440 --> 00:45:12.640
in the upper part of your abdomen
and press it on the stomach.

00:45:12.640 --> 00:45:18.320
Now here you have to say
with full confidence,

00:45:18.320 --> 00:45:25.040
to help the Kundalini to rise,
Mother, I am my own master.

00:45:25.040 --> 00:45:27.280
This you have to say ten times.

00:45:27.280 --> 00:45:30.320
These are the ten commandments
which you have to say,

00:45:30.320 --> 00:45:35.055
that Mother, I am my own master.

00:46:11.440 --> 00:46:17.840
Now, ten times with full confidence.

00:46:18.800 --> 00:46:27.920
Now please raise your right hand
to your heart.

00:46:27.920 --> 00:46:34.800
Now here you have to say,
again with full confidence,

00:46:34.800 --> 00:46:37.200
Mother, I am the Spirit.

00:46:37.200 --> 00:46:39.600
This is the truth, you are the Spirit.

00:46:39.600 --> 00:46:45.040
But you have to say with full confidence,
Mother, I am the Spirit.

00:46:46.000 --> 00:46:49.796
This you have to say twelve times.

00:47:17.280 --> 00:47:24.400
Now one has to know
that God Almighty is the ocean of love.

00:47:24.400 --> 00:47:29.280
But above all He is the ocean
of forgiveness.

00:47:29.280 --> 00:47:31.120
So He forgives.

00:47:31.120 --> 00:47:33.760
Whatever wrong you do He forgives.

00:47:33.760 --> 00:47:41.440
So don't feel guilty
and put your right hand across

00:47:41.440 --> 00:47:49.920
on the left hand side in the corner
which is made by your neck and your shoulder.

00:47:49.920 --> 00:47:54.080
Now here you have to say
again with full confidence,

00:47:54.080 --> 00:47:57.840
sixteen times, Mother, I am not guilty.

00:47:57.840 --> 00:48:01.120
Please say it, Mother, I am not guilty.

00:48:01.120 --> 00:48:04.560
Sixteen times.

00:48:04.560 --> 00:48:07.923
I am not guilty at all.

00:48:07.923 --> 00:48:16.059
Please say it.

00:48:46.080 --> 00:48:55.600
Now raise your hand across on your forehead
and it's a very important center.

00:48:55.600 --> 00:49:06.400
Here you have to say from your heart,
Mother, I forgive everyone.

00:49:06.400 --> 00:49:08.640
Please say it from your heart.

00:49:08.640 --> 00:49:10.720
How many times is not the point.

00:49:10.720 --> 00:49:15.120
Mother, I forgive everyone.

00:49:15.120 --> 00:49:18.800
Now some would say
that it's very difficult to forgive.

00:49:18.800 --> 00:49:24.720
But it's a myth
that we do not forgive or we forgive.

00:49:24.720 --> 00:49:27.600
We do not do anything
in both the cases.

00:49:27.600 --> 00:49:31.600
But if we don't forgive
then we play into wrong hands.

00:49:31.600 --> 00:49:38.588
So please say from your heart,
Mother, I forgive everyone.

00:49:46.000 --> 00:49:53.200
Now please take your hand on the back agnya,
the same center, on the back side of your head

00:49:53.200 --> 00:49:58.240
and allow your head to rest on it
and push it back a little bit.

00:49:59.040 --> 00:50:05.600
Now here you have to say
for your satisfaction,

00:50:05.600 --> 00:50:12.080
because you always feel guilty,
that, O Divine, if I have done anything wrong,

00:50:12.080 --> 00:50:15.390
please forgive me.

00:50:21.200 --> 00:50:29.600
Please forgive me, from your heart.

00:50:29.600 --> 00:50:36.160
Stretch your hand fully
and put your center of your palm

00:50:36.160 --> 00:50:44.960
on top of the fontanel bone area,
which was a very soft bone in your childhood.

00:50:44.960 --> 00:50:46.160
Press it hard.

00:50:46.160 --> 00:50:49.680
Press hard your scalp.

00:50:49.680 --> 00:50:55.920
Now you have to move it seven times
saying one thing, which you have to ask for,

00:50:55.920 --> 00:51:01.200
Mother, please give us My Self-realization,
because I cannot force on you.

00:51:01.200 --> 00:51:03.920
So you have to ask for it.

00:51:03.920 --> 00:51:12.480
Seven times press it hard
and move it seven times very hard.

00:51:12.480 --> 00:51:16.774
Slowly saying that.
